msgstr "分類顯示"

msgid "Brand Display"
msgstr "品牌顯示"

msgid "Searchable Content Types"
msgstr "可搜尋的內容類型"

msgid "Choose which content types to include in search results."
msgstr "選擇要包含在搜尋結果中的內容類型。"

msgid ""
"Configure which additional content fields to include in the search index."
msgstr "設定要包含在搜尋索引中的額外內容欄位。"

msgid "Fuzzy Matching (Typo Tolerance)"
msgstr "模糊匹配（容錯拼寫）"

msgid "Configure how tolerant the search is to spelling mistakes and typos."
msgstr "設定搜尋對拼寫錯誤和打字錯誤的容忍度。"

msgid ""
"Adjust how much each field contributes to search relevance. Higher values "
"mean more importance."
msgstr "調整每個欄位對搜尋相關性的影響程度。較高的值表示更重要。"

msgid "Cache Settings"
msgstr "快取設定"

msgid "Configure how long search results are cached for faster performance."
msgstr "設定搜尋結果的緩存時間以提高效能。"

msgid "Analytics & Tracking"
msgstr "分析與追蹤"

msgid "Configure what search data to collect for analytics."
msgstr "設定要為分析收集哪些搜尋資料。"

msgid "Save Settings"
msgstr "儲存設定"

msgid "Search Synonyms"
msgstr "搜尋同義詞"

msgid ""
"Synonyms allow search queries to match related terms. For example, 'laptop' "
"can also match 'notebook' and 'portable computer'."
msgstr ""
"同義詞允許搜尋查詢匹配相關詞彙。例如，'筆電'也可以匹配'筆記型電腦'和'行動電"
"腦'。"

msgid "Filter by term..."
msgstr "依關鍵字篩選..."

msgid "All Languages"
msgstr "所有語言"

msgid "Loading synonyms..."
msgstr "正在載入同義詞..."

msgid "Search Engine Setup"
msgstr "搜尋引擎設定"

msgid "Configure a new search engine for your store in a few simple steps."
msgstr "透過幾個簡單步驟為您的商店配置新的搜尋引擎。"

msgid "Basic Info"
msgstr "基本資訊"

msgid "Review"
msgstr "審核"

msgid ""
"Give your search engine a name and identifier. The slug will be used in URLs "
"and API calls."
msgstr "為您的搜尋引擎命名並指定識別碼。slug 將用於 URL 和 API 呼叫。"

msgid "Engine Name"
msgstr "引擎名稱"

msgid "e.g., Shop Search, Blog Search"
msgstr "例如：Shop Search, Blog Search"

msgid "A friendly name to identify this search engine."
msgstr "用來識別此搜尋引擎的友好名稱。"

msgid "e.g., shop-search, blog-search"
msgstr "例如：shop-search, blog-search"

msgid "URL-safe identifier. Leave blank to auto-generate from the name."
msgstr "URL 安全的識別碼。留空將會根據名稱自動產生。"

msgid "Inactive engines won't be available for search queries."
msgstr "未啟用的引擎將無法用於搜尋查詢。"

msgid "Tip"
msgstr "提示"

msgid ""
"You can create multiple engines for different purposes. For example, a 'Shop "
"Search' for products and a 'Blog Search' for articles."
msgstr ""
"您可以為不同用途建立多個引擎。例如，為商品建立「商店搜尋」，為文章建立「部落"
"格搜尋」。"

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "下一步"

msgid ""
"Select which content types this search engine will index and include in "
"results."
msgstr "選擇此搜尋引擎要索引並包含在結果中的內容類型。"

msgid "Note"
msgstr "注意"

msgid ""
"Leave all unchecked to search all content types. Select specific types to "
"limit what this engine searches."
msgstr "全部不勾選以搜尋所有內容類型。選擇特定類型以限制此引擎的搜尋範圍。"

msgid "Back"
msgstr "返回"

msgid ""
"Optionally customize how different fields contribute to search relevance. "
"Higher values mean more importance."
msgstr "可選擇自訂不同欄位對搜尋相關性的影響。較高的值表示更重要。"

msgid "Use custom weights for this engine"
msgstr "為此引擎使用自訂權重"

msgid ""
"When disabled, the engine uses the global weight settings from Search "
"Settings."
msgstr "當停用時，引擎將使用來自搜尋設定的全域權重設定。"

msgid "Weight Configuration"
msgstr "權重配置"

msgid ""
"Higher weights (up to 2.0) make matches in that field more important. A "
"weight of 0 excludes the field from relevance scoring. Default values work "
"well for most use cases."
msgstr ""
"較高的權重（最高為 2.0）會使該欄位的匹配結果更重要。權重為 0 會將該欄位排除在"
"相關性評分之外。預設值對於大多數使用案例來說效果良好。"

msgid "Review & Create"
msgstr "審核並建立"

msgid "Review your search engine configuration before creating it."
msgstr "在建立搜尋引擎之前請審核您的設定。"

msgid "Name:"
msgstr "名稱："

msgid "Slug:"
msgstr "Slug："

msgid "Status:"
msgstr "狀態:"

msgid "All Content Types"
msgstr "所有內容類型"

msgid "default:"
msgstr "預設："

msgid "Using global weight settings from Search Settings."
msgstr "使用來自搜尋設定的全域權重設定。"

msgid "Ready to create"
msgstr "準備建立"

msgid ""
"Click 'Create Engine' to create this search engine. You can edit the "
"configuration later, including adding category and brand exclusions."
msgstr ""
"點擊「建立引擎」來建立此搜尋引擎。您可以稍後編輯設定，包括新增類別和品牌排"
"除。"

msgid "Create Engine"
msgstr "建立引擎"

